# AWS Project 2: Automated Backup System

## Python EBS Snapshot

```python
import boto3

ec2 = boto3.client(
    "ec2"
)

volumes = [

    "vol-111111",
    "vol-222222"
]

for volume in volumes:

    ec2.create_snapshot(

        VolumeId=volume,

        Description=
        "Daily Backup"

    )

    print(
        volume,
        "Snapshot Created"
    )
```

---

# Delete Old Snapshots

```python
import boto3

ec2 = boto3.client("ec2")

snapshots = ec2.describe_snapshots(

    OwnerIds=["self"]

)

for snapshot in snapshots["Snapshots"]:

    print(
        snapshot["SnapshotId"]
    )
```

