# Cost Optimization Project

## EC2 Rightsizing

### Python

```python
import boto3

cloudwatch =
boto3.client(
    "cloudwatch"
)

ec2 =
boto3.client("ec2")

instances =
ec2.describe_instances()

for reservation in instances[
    "Reservations"
]:

    for instance in reservation[
        "Instances"
    ]:

        print(

            instance[
                "InstanceId"
            ]

        )
```

Identify underutilized servers and move:

```text
t3.large
      ↓
t3.micro
```

---

# S3 Lifecycle Cost Reduction

```python
import boto3

s3 =
boto3.client("s3")

s3.put_bucket_lifecycle_configuration(

    Bucket="company-site",

    LifecycleConfiguration={

        "Rules":[

            {

                "ID":"Archive",

                "Status":"Enabled",

                "Transitions":[

                    {

                        "Days":30,

                        "StorageClass":
                        "GLACIER"

                    }

                ]

            }

        ]

    }

)
```

