# Multi-Tier AWS Application (Hinglish + Code)

## Project Overview (Interview Explanation)

### Hinglish

Maine AWS par ek **highly available multi-tier web application** deploy ki thi jisme:

* Amazon VPC use karke secure network banaya.
* EC2 instances par application host ki.
* Application Load Balancer (ALB) use karke traffic distribute kiya.
* Auto Scaling use karke load ke according servers automatically add/remove kiye.
* Amazon RDS me database host kiya.
* Amazon S3 me static files aur backups store kiye.
* CloudFront CDN aur Route 53 use karke fast content delivery aur DNS management implement kiya.
* Python (Boto3) se infrastructure automation kiya.

