# 1. Create VPC

### Python

```python
import boto3

ec2 = boto3.client("ec2")

response = ec2.create_vpc(

    CidrBlock="10.0.0.0/16"

)

print(

    "VPC ID:",

    response["Vpc"]["VpcId"]

)
```

### Hinglish

Ye code AWS me ek private network create karta hai jiska CIDR block 10.0.0.0/16 hai.

